<html>
<head>
<title>Contents of Education Spotlight</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/paper2.jpg">
<center>
<h2>Monday, September 11, 1995<br>
</h2>
</center>
<hr>
<br>
<center>
<h3>Bureacrats vs. Parents</h3><p>
